    By default, this UI framework should support the following inputs:

    • form
    • button
    • checkbox
    • date
    • datetime-local
    • email
    • number
    • select/options
    • radio buttons
    • text
    • textarea
    • url
    • video.controls

    Provide the html for the following state types:

    • input
    • video
